{
  "text": "Furthermore, the balanced scorecard model for enterprises supports the idea of including the customers as part of the activity [CITATION_1] . The Common Good Theory and the balanced scorecard support the principles of the Co-creation Theory, where the customers specify the value of the activity [CITATION_2] ",
